raw 15 live "no hardcoding — values belong in SSOT"
  slug no-hardcode
  enforce tool/no_hardcode_lint.hexa
  scope magic numbers, paths, URLs, hostnames, credentials, API keys, version strings, tuning constants, timeouts
  opt-out @const (named constant with reason) + .hardcode-baseline (grandfather drift)
  defer-until 2026-06
  why Hardcoded values hide the source of truth and fossilize assumptions. Relocate to .ext (external resource), .own (project rule), or named const with @const marker. Unexplained literals = invisible contract. 2026-04-21 defer-until 2026-06 추가 — status=live 유지하되 실효 enforce 는 보류 (literal scanner 미완성 + 354 violation triage 미완료로 raw_all bypass 에서 31 회 반복 exclude). 2026-06 재평가: scanner 완성 + baseline 완비 시 enforce 복귀.
  proof tool/no_hardcode_lint.hexa
  follow-up no_hardcode_lint.hexa implementation — literal scanner + whitelist (0, 1, -1, empty string, small bounds in hot kernels) + .hardcode-baseline grandfather list
  follow-up 2026-06 재평가 — scanner 완성도 + triage 진척 측정 후 (a) defer-until 연장, (b) status=live 실효화, (c) status=deferred 로 전환 중 택일

